quizzes.question:
What output results from the following code?
<?php 
$a = 7; $b = 3; 
$a += $b;
echo $a;
?>

quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Assignment Operators[/h1]

[b]Assignment[/b] operators work with numeric values to write values to variables.[code format="php" ]$num1 = 5;
$num2 = $num1;[/code]
[b]$num1[/b] and [b]$num2[/b] now contain the value of 5. 

Assignments can also be used in conjunction with arithmetic operators. [img id="2359" width="100%"]
[b]Example:[/b] [code format="php" codeId="471"]<?php
 $x = 50;
 $x += 100;
 echo $x;

 // Outputs: [b]150[/b]
?> [/code]
